Sold by @Prestige_Tony 🔑😍 
Gated community in the heart of South Beach! Modern 5 bedroom home with 5 full bathrooms. 3 bedrooms on 2nd floor plus one full bedroom and gym/office on first level. 2-car garage, private pool with outdoor kitchen. Located on gated Palm Island in the heart of #SouthBeach 🌴

Listed by @PaulBensonEV 🔑✨
Timeless, elegant mountain living on just over 12 acres in the exclusive gated Glenwild Golf Community. ⛰️ Designed by renowned architect Mike Upwall, this masterpiece inspires to create memories with family and friends to last a lifetime in a home designed to entertain. 😍 Only 10 minutes from world class skiing, 15 minutes to Park City's historic Main Street for fine dining & exclusive shopping, and 30 minutes to SLC International Airport ⛷️

Contact @PaulBensonEV for more information! 🔑
-
